(DDINTERACT 2 DOC)	~(the doctor wants to interact with parry)

(DBABNORMAL 2 DOC)	~(the doctor thinks parry is crazy)

(DBEXCITED 2 DOC)	~(the doctor thinks parry is excited)

(DBHELP 2 DOC)		~(the doctor thinks parry wants (needs) help)



