~ ( INTENTIONS -- IN REVERSE PRIORITY ORDER  )


(PINTERACT 5 INN)	~ ( parry wants to interact with the interviewer)

(PGAMES 1 INN)		~ ( parry wants to comment on the doctors games)

(PFACTS 1 INN)		~ ( parry wants to comment on the doctors asking so many facts)

(PMAFIA 0 INN)		~ ( parry wants to comment on the doctors mafia connections)

(PHELP 2 INN)		~ ( parry wants to get help, to cure his nervousness by telling about bookies)

(PTELL 1 INN)		~ ( parry wants to tell his delusions)

(PCONFIRM 1 INN)	~ ( parry wants to get confirmation for his delusions)

(PSELF 0 INN)		~ ( parry wants to comment on the encounter situation)

(PSTOP 0 INN)		~ ( parry wants to stop now )

(PSTRONGFEEL 0 INN)	~ ( parry needs to take care of his strong emotions)

(PPARANOIA 0 INN)	~ ( parry is controlled by his emotion of shame)

(PONTOP 1 INN)		~ ( parry wants to get on top of the situation)

(PGETBACK 1 INN)	~ ( parry wants to get back at someone who has antagonized him)

(PSUFFER 0 INN)		~ ( parry wants to withdraw and suffer)

(PEXIT 0 INN) 		~ ( parry wants to leave)

